description:
KRyLack Password Recovery v2.73.02 made Portable.

No need to install it!

Or, if you want to, setup and Serial are included.


KRyLack Password Recovery is a program to recover lost or forgotten passwords to files of the following types: ZIP, RAR (including v3.x, SFX, multi-volume and archives with encrypted filenames) and ACE archives

More infos at:
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.krylack.com/KLPassRec/index.htm&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.krylack.com/KLPassRec/index.htm&lt;/a&gt;


This package contains a first Portable version built using RunHiddenConsole.exe to start the Batch file that changes some values in Registry, runs the program and deletes the Registry values when exiting from the program just to avoid having the sloppy DOS window in the background. Some AVs complain with it recognizing RunHiddenConsole.exe as a malicious/potentially harmful program as it can be used to hide malicious behaviours. If it&amp;#039;s your case, or just don&amp;#039;t trust in the first one, use the second version.


The Portable SFX EXE files are built up using WinRAR. you can use it to extract the files and check them one by one if you want to be sure of what is running on your machine.


